14JUL2017 Automation Meeting

What information are we pulling? Checklist:
-count, unit (10 plates)
       -e.g. plates, tubes, samples, cells, etc.
-method name
-Date (start/end time) 
-status (completed, in prog, not started)
-phase, current step ("5 plates have started phase 4")
-Flask/rest to talk to the server on client side
-Live refresh?
-Birds eye map of devices?
-ERROR button to automatically send an email to automation team
-fields to add systems
-each system w/ a unique identifier, short description
-preview (last 5 processes/runs)
-be able to sort through table (all failed, paused, completed, etc)
